- Always use the theme system for component styling (see `THEME_SYSTEM.md`)
- Always use the utility functions for dynamic styling (colors, variants, etc.)
- Always test components for syntax errors.
- Always use semantic color names rather than specific color values.
- Always run the server and client using `npm run dev`.
- Do NOT create markdown files to explain your changes unless asked to do so
- Project documentation is located in the documentation folder 